along with chesapeake energy was one of the two major producers in southcentral kansas appealed the order but soon went into bankruptcy in  the company went through a chapter  bankruptcy reorganization operationsedit in the third quarter of  the company produced  thousand barrels of oil equivalent  gj per day sandridge owns oil properties in the midcontinent which accounts for  of production it also owns properties in the permian basin west texas and in the niobrara formation of colorado the company has formed  public royalty trusts sandridge permian trust nyse per  owner of royalty interests in oil and natural gas properties in the central basin platform of the permian basin in andrews county texas sandridge mississippian trust i nyse sdt  owner of royalty interests in oil and natural gas properties in the mississippian formation in alfalfa garfield grant and woods counties in oklahoma sandridge mississippian trust ii nyse sdr  owner of royalty interests in oil and natural gas properties in the mississippian formation in alfalfa grant kay noble and woods counties in northern oklahoma and barber comanche harper and sumner counties in southern kansas referencesedit  a b c d e f g sandridge energy inc form q quarterly report  richard finger february   tom ward of sandridge energy another ceo thats got to go forbes magazine   sandridge energy inc prices initial public offering press release prnewswire november     sandridge energy board ousts founder tom ward cnbc june     sandridge management team  sandridge to sell gulf of mexico business for  million bloomberg lp january     sandridge energy inc announces acquisition of pinon gathering company llc press release prnewswire october     sandridge energy inc acquires north park basin niobrara shale oil assets for  million in cash prnewswire november     downward flows ripples oil gas downturn hitting counties on many levels kansas agland amy bickel feb   retrieved  march   fracking divides small town of anthony kansas u